rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
So I bought some Tasty
Kordeth Samod for my
girlfriend on the way home.

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
One bite of it and she was
back to her old chirpy self!

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
She probably found it a refreshing
new taste, 'cos she'd never eaten
anything from Luxuria before.

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Kordeth's a type of sausage, you
know. I tried a bit myself too,
and it really is good stuff!

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0005
rows.name:
There's this succulent juiciness
when your teeth sink in. It
really works well in Samod.

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Best part is, trying out new food
gave us something fun to talk about!

rows.label: tlk45300011_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Ahh, I'm so glad that Avaritia's
managed to expand its trade
with all these countries...
